= Copy Abilities =

This page documents all copy abilities in Kirby's Adventure for the NES.

== Overview ==

Kirby's Adventure introduced the Copy Ability system that would become a staple of the franchise. Kirby can inhale enemies and copy their powers by swallowing them.

