== Detailed Ability Information ==

=== Backdrop (ID: $01) ===

A wrestling-style ability:
* Grab enemies by pressing B next to them
* Slam them into the ground
* Can defeat multiple enemies at once

'''Source Enemies:'''
* Bugzzy (mini-boss)

=== Ball (ID: $02) ===

Transform into a bouncy ball:
* Press B to transform
* Bounces off walls and ceilings
* Hard to control but invincible

'''Source Enemies:'''
* Bubbles

=== Beam (ID: $03) ===

Whip-like energy beam:
* Press B for short-range beam whip
* Can hit enemies through walls (sometimes)
* Good all-around ability

'''Source Enemies:'''
* Waddle Doo

=== Crash (ID: $04) ===

Powerful one-time screen clear:
* Press B to use
* Destroys all enemies on screen
* Ability is lost after use
* Save for tough situations

'''Source Enemies:'''
* Bomber
* Scarfy (when angry)

=== Cutter (ID: $05) ===

Boomerang blade attack:
* Press B to throw blade
* Returns to Kirby
* Can hit enemies on return

'''Source Enemies:'''
* Sir Kibble

